### 회원가입 테스트
POST http://localhost:6000/users/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "loginId": "testuser",
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 로그인 테스트
# @name login
POST http://localhost:6000/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "loginId": "testuser",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 응답에서 access_token 추출
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.access_token}}
@refreshToken = {{login.response.body.refresh_token}}

### 프로필 조회 테스트 (보호된 리소스)
GET http://localhost:6000/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 토큰 갱신 테스트
# @name refresh
POST http://localhost:6000/users/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh_token": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### 새로운 access_token으로 프로필 조회
@newAccessToken = {{refresh.response.body.access_token}}
GET http://localhost:6000/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{newAccessToken}}